subject: Bathroom graffiti (was: what is j unit?)
msgSnippet: Unfortunately, the camera phone was in my pocket, its memory is full, and I was busy holding a toddler on the potty.  But I did think about it... David Saff
messageBody:
Unfortunately, the camera phone was in my pocket, its memory is full,
and I was busy holding a toddler on the potty. But I did think about it...

David Saff

>
